UID:bgPKJ30piClPMP-ZefGuu
SUMMARY:Eastside Coffee Outside Every Wednesday Morning
DTSTAMP:20260307T070346Z
DTSTART:20260311T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:Eastside Coffee Outside Every Wednesday Morning Drop by to join
	 us ANY Wednesday\, rain or shine\, for a chat\, a snack\, and something h
	ot to drink. No RSVP necessary.  You'll find us  Every Wednesday\,  7:00 A
	M to 9:30 AM Rotary Central Station \\(the picnic shelter\\) 1 Railroad Av
	e\, Kirkland\, WA 98033 Anna brings her fresh-baked vegan muffins to share
	. Dylan often brews different varieties of loose-leaf tea to share. Kurt b
	rews regular and decaf coffee and brings hot water\, tea bags\, and hot co
	coa packets. Bring your pup for a treat\, too!  We're here from 7-9:30am\,
	 but you can stop by for as much or as little of that time as works for yo
	u. It's on the Cross Kirkland Corridor\, so it's easily accessible for wal
	kers\, joggers\, bikers\, and by car. There are reusable mugs available\, 
	or bring your own.  Hope to see you ANY or EVERY Wednesday morning!\n\nhtt
	ps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/eastside-coffee-outside-every-w
	ednesday-morning/18291034/2026-03-11T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/eastside-coffee-outside-e
	very-wednesday-morning/18291034/2026-03-11T00
LOCATION:Rotary Central Station Picnic Shelter\, 1 Railroad Avenue\, Kirkla
	nd\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
