DTSTAMP:20260307T070346Z
DTSTART:20260314T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an unforgettable evening of wine and cuisine as we 
	partner with Heritage Restaurant for a weekly dining experience at Evergre
	en Family Wines. Each Friday\, Heritage’s culinary team will present a bea
	utifully crafted three-course menu designed to showcase the flavors of the
	 season and paired perfectly with our hand-selected Evergreen Family wines
	. \n\nEach course highlights local ingredients and thoughtful preparation\
	, creating a seamless journey of flavor and harmony between the kitchen an
	d the cellar. The menu will remain the same throughout the season\, allowi
	ng guests to savor and revisit this distinctive pairing experience. \n\nDo
	ors open at 6:00 PM for a welcome pour\, followed by dinner service beginn
	ing promptly at 6:30 PM. Enjoy an evening of exceptional wine\, elevated c
	uisine\, and warm hospitality in the heart of Woodinville’s wine country. 
	\n\nClub-members: $90 per person | Non-members: $100 per person | Reservat
	ions Required\n\n\\(Price includes three courses and wine pairings\; tax a
	nd gratuity not included.\\) \n\nA $25 per person reservation fee is requi
	red to book and will be applied toward your total at the end of the evenin
	g. \n\nPlease add a note in the dietary restrictions box if multiple entre
	es types are desired in a single booking. Thank you!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6
	amcity.com/events/#/details/paired-dinner-experience/17806350/2026-03-13T0
	0\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
